@startuml Pay Request Fees
!theme plain
autonumber

actor Student
actor Cashier
participant "Student Dashboard" as StudentUI
participant "Cashier Dashboard" as CashierUI
participant "Payment Service" as Payment
participant "DocumentRequest" as Request
participant "SystemCounter" as Counter
participant "CollectionLog" as CollectionLog
participant "Xendit API" as Xendit
participant "Notification Service" as Notify

Student -> StudentUI : Click Pay for request batch
StudentUI -> Payment : pay_with_xendit(batch_id, delivery_scope)
Payment -> Request : Load payable requests
Payment -> Xendit : Create invoice
Xendit --> Payment : invoice URL / reference
Payment --> StudentUI : Redirect to hosted payment page

Xendit -> Payment : Payment webhook callback
Payment -> Request : Update status to PENDING_CASHIER_APPROVAL
Payment -> Counter : get_next_receipt_no()
Counter --> Payment : receipt no
Payment -> CollectionLog : Create provisional collection log
Payment -> Notify : Send payment confirmation notice

Cashier -> CashierUI : Verify payment and issue receipt
CashierUI -> Request : Confirm payment batch
Request -> CollectionLog : Finalize payment record
CashierUI -> Notify : Notify student that payment is verified

@enduml
